commit.message:
[cloudpinyin] use cloud unicode char as place holder.

Now font can handle this char much better, so we use this by default.
[cloudpinyin] Clean up the code and avoid crash when there's no data.

[cloudpinyin] set timeout, increase max handle but don't allow overflow.

1. easy handle is not correctly set with timeout when request string
2. some people reports that cloudpinyin may use a lot of memory when
there is error. Possibly due to the unlimited request and no timeout.

This change should helps people to recover from cloudpinyin error much
faster and has a deterministic bound on memory.
[translate] use glob to match po file
[cloudpinyin] make baidu use https, seems it works.
